### Step 2

Apply my palette.

<pre>
mkdir with-palette
for SRC in $(ls -1 downloads); do
  convert downloads/$SRC -map palette.png with-palette/$SRC
done
</pre>

![palettised](/content/images/2017/01/palettised.png)

